text:
Just saw this movie. 8 thoughts about Episode 8
1 Holy shit it was super long
2 Fuck everything about Casino planet. Every possible thing. 
3 Star Destroyers unable to kill a puny ship for over 18 hours is asking a lot from my suspension of disbelief
4 Leia coming back to life was pretty dumb
5 Where are the other Knights of Ren, Ben?
6 Lightspeed through the Dreadnought was a damn sexy shot
7 The final shot with lightsaberbroomkid was dumb and bad
8 WHAT IS LESSON THREE? (This is only an issue if unaddressed in IX, but I expect they'll address it)
